00:02:00.720 --> 00:02:02.300
-Head constable Zheng.
-Yes?

35
00:02:02.300 --> 00:02:06.830
I came to say goodbye.

36
00:02:10.340 --> 00:02:12.830
What do you mean?

37
00:02:12.830 --> 00:02:15.320
You aren't running Miaosheng Restaurant anymore?

38
00:02:15.320 --> 00:02:17.760
Are you not pursuing Advisor Tan anymore?

39
00:02:19.030 --> 00:02:23.410
You're renouncing the marriage contract?

40
00:02:24.860 --> 00:02:26.870
It's not that I'm not pursuing anymore.

41
00:02:28.050 --> 00:02:30.280
It's just that I see clearly now.

42
00:02:32.600 --> 00:02:35.060
My marriage with Miss.

43
00:02:35.860 --> 00:02:38.830
It was an arranged marriage.

44
00:02:38.830 --> 00:02:40.910
The words of a matchmaker.

45
00:02:41.530 --> 00:02:43.620
I still remember.

46
00:02:45.220 --> 00:02:47.670
When I first saw her,

47
00:02:49.000 --> 00:02:52.250
it was the morning of the fifth day of the first month.

48
00:02:53.260 --> 00:02:55.090
She

49
00:02:55.960 --> 00:02:59.420
secretly climbed the wall from the backyard into the Tan house.

50
00:02:59.420 --> 00:03:02.280
Her father caught her red-handed!

51
00:03:04.260 --> 00:03:06.340
With her smile,

52
00:03:07.950 --> 00:03:11.540
the winter's first plum flowers blossomed.

53
00:03:15.650 --> 00:03:18.760
The flower in my heart also bloomed.

54
00:03:19.610 --> 00:03:24.200
Even now, I couldn't bear to pick it out.

55
00:03:29.890 --> 00:03:31.670
-Brother Zhu.
-Yes?

56
00:03:32.930 --> 00:03:34.840
I never thought

57
00:03:34.840 --> 00:03:38.660
you would be someone who cherishes flowers.

58
00:03:39.350 --> 00:03:44.340
So, no matter how much she rejects me

59
00:03:44.930 --> 00:03:47.130
I'm always thinking

60
00:03:49.110 --> 00:03:52.680
that if I can hold onto the flower in my heart,

61
00:03:54.330 --> 00:03:57.030
then she will be moved by actions.

62
00:03:58.330 --> 00:04:02.960
But just like what you said, the only person I have moved

63
00:04:02.960 --> 00:04:05.140
there's only me.

64
00:04:09.160 --> 00:04:13.930
Before, I thought she came here to

65
00:04:13.930 --> 00:04:16.180
avoid me.

66
00:04:16.930 --> 00:04:19.980
Until today, I finally understood.

67
00:04:19.980 --> 00:04:23.160
She actually liked staying here.


69
00:04:39.820 --> 00:04:42.130
This is the marriage contract.

70
00:04:53.320 --> 00:04:57.720
Please give this to Lord Tang.

71
00:05:03.780 --> 00:05:05.600
From now on,

72
00:05:06.450 --> 00:05:08.960
my marriage with Linyin

73
00:05:09.790 --> 00:05:12.010
is finished.

74
00:05:13.820 --> 00:05:15.600
Brother Zhu.

75
00:05:15.600 --> 00:05:17.290
In the future,

76
00:05:17.840 --> 00:05:20.050
we'll respectively marry other people and

77
00:05:21.830 --> 00:05:24.390
will have nothing to do with each other.

78
00:05:29.420 --> 00:05:33.230
When Lord Tang sees this

79
00:05:33.230 --> 00:05:34.800
he will definitely

80
00:05:35.350 --> 00:05:37.360
feel better again.

81
00:05:40.560 --> 00:05:42.850
I'll give you a gift.

82
00:05:48.070 --> 00:05:50.830
This is Miss Ruyi's contract.

83
00:05:52.150 --> 00:05:53.800
You

84
00:05:53.800 --> 00:05:57.340
never paid the 500 taels.

85
00:05:58.870 --> 00:06:00.560
However,

86
00:06:02.010 --> 00:06:07.510
I give you guys my blessings. Lovers will always have a happy ending.

87
00:06:09.030 --> 00:06:13.450
You and Miss Ruyi must stay well.

88
00:06:13.450 --> 00:06:15.380
Thank you.

89
00:06:18.460 --> 00:06:20.680
But I'm afraid this contract...

90
00:06:22.560 --> 00:06:24.760
There isn't any use.

91
00:06:32.540 --> 00:06:35.170
Brother Zhu, you are a good person.

92
00:06:35.170 --> 00:06:37.600
I recognize you as my brother.

93
00:06:37.600 --> 00:06:40.810
If you have any problems in the future,
you can always tell me.

94
00:06:40.810 --> 00:06:42.370
Okay.

95
00:06:42.370 --> 00:06:43.850
You

96
00:06:44.480 --> 00:06:46.550
are going back to Jinan?

97
00:06:47.970 --> 00:06:49.850
Yes.

98
00:06:49.850 --> 00:06:54.460
I can't help with anything here.

99
00:06:55.790 --> 00:06:57.580
I even caused trouble for fianc—

100
00:06:58.280 --> 00:07:00.580
for her.

101
00:07:03.110 --> 00:07:04.710
Brother Zhu.

102
00:07:05.670 --> 00:07:11.400
Are you not going to say goodbye to Advisor Tan?

103
00:07:17.140 --> 00:07:18.720
No.

104
00:07:21.620 --> 00:07:24.400
Ever since Lord Tang got hurt,

105
00:07:25.600 --> 00:07:28.250
she has been sad.

106
00:07:29.540 --> 00:07:33.670
I am not going to stay here and trouble her anymore.

107
00:07:38.030 --> 00:07:39.610
Brother Zhu.

108
00:07:40.560 --> 00:07:44.340
You have liked her at some point.

109
00:07:46.350 --> 00:07:48.200
If you sadly walk away like this,

110
00:07:48.200 --> 00:07:50.610
the sincere effort you put in...

111
00:07:51.990 --> 00:07:54.390
how is that good?

112
00:07:59.930 --> 00:08:02.750
What you said is correct.

113
00:08:08.030 --> 00:08:09.700
Brother Zheng.

114
00:08:10.530 --> 00:08:15.530
Make sure to say hi when you come to Jinan.

115
00:08:16.570 --> 00:08:18.160
We will

116
00:08:18.940 --> 00:08:21.200
meet soon.

117
00:08:58.800 --> 00:08:59.950
Miss.

118
00:08:59.950 --> 00:09:00.920
Dacong?

119
00:09:00.920 --> 00:09:02.600
Do you have time today?

120
00:09:02.600 --> 00:09:05.850
I don't have time today. Can we talk another time?

121
00:09:06.400 --> 00:09:12.900
There's no another time. I am going back to Jinan today.

122
00:09:13.610 --> 00:09:15.390
This sudden?

123
00:09:16.130 --> 00:09:19.970
Can I treat you to a meal?

124
00:09:31.500 --> 00:09:33.560
Let's go eat and chat.

125
00:09:33.560 --> 00:09:35.060
Okay.

126
00:09:44.100 --> 00:09:46.200
Why did you bring me to this place to eat?

127
00:09:46.200 --> 00:09:48.530
Because there's food you like to eat here.

128
00:09:48.530 --> 00:09:53.820
Miss, look. Does that kite look like the one
we played with when we were young?

129
00:09:53.820 --> 00:09:55.650
It does.

130
