134
00:10:18.590 --> 00:10:23.000
But you like to eat pig liver from these road-side stalls.

135
00:10:27.270 --> 00:10:29.460
You thought it through?

136
00:10:34.300 --> 00:10:37.130
I already gave Sir Tang the marriage contract.

137
00:10:38.150 --> 00:10:43.300
When I get back to Jinan, I will explain it to our parents.

138
00:10:45.800 --> 00:10:50.520
Miss, I actually tried.

139
00:10:51.330 --> 00:10:57.200
If there's someone to blame, blame the heavens for letting us meet but not letting us love.

140
00:10:57.200 --> 00:10:59.570
You're actually pretty good.

141
00:11:00.450 --> 00:11:04.380
Although you're spoiled, you'll never hurt anyone.

142
00:11:04.380 --> 00:11:08.500
Wait a minute! You should stop talking. I...I was finally able to...

143
00:11:08.500 --> 00:11:12.040
I have already decided to leave but with your words you're pulling me back.

144
00:11:12.040 --> 00:11:15.930
Also, I don't understand you.

145
00:11:15.930 --> 00:11:21.410
Once you decide on someone, not even 8 horses can pull you back.

146
00:11:22.940 --> 00:11:27.840
You're too good for that...let's not mention him!

147
00:11:28.480 --> 00:11:31.960
Then eat more, I'll treat you.

148
00:11:33.300 --> 00:11:36.600
Qingchen and I will play with the kite
with you when we go to Jinan.

149
00:11:36.600 --> 00:11:41.400
Not another time, let's play with it today.

150
00:11:41.400 --> 00:11:42.920
Now?

151
00:11:43.850 --> 00:11:45.160
Yes.

152
00:11:54.700 --> 00:12:00.900
Does this one look good?
This one or this one? This one?

153
00:12:02.760 --> 00:12:04.120
Okay, I'll take this one.

154
00:12:04.120 --> 00:12:06.250
-Okay.
-Thank you.

155
00:12:10.040 --> 00:12:12.170
Run faster.

156
00:12:12.170 --> 00:12:15.510
Miss, slow down.

157
00:12:16.390 --> 00:12:18.710
This kite flew really high up.

158
00:12:19.610 --> 00:12:22.260
It was all thanks to Miss who taught me when were young.

159
00:12:25.840 --> 00:12:31.550
I was stupid then that I only learned how now.

160
00:12:33.520 --> 00:12:37.190
Miss, look.

161
00:12:46.630 --> 00:12:49.190
I'm not trying to be clingy.

162
00:12:51.350 --> 00:12:53.140
This kite

163
00:12:55.980 --> 00:12:58.410
is one of my memories.

164
00:13:02.240 --> 00:13:03.920
Today.

165
00:13:06.210 --> 00:13:08.570
Let the story of husband Zhu Dacong

166
