00:17:15.700 --> 00:17:17.110
Assitant Zhou is back.

201
00:17:17.110 --> 00:17:21.310
Where is the Lord and Xiao Liu? Who are these people?

202
00:17:21.310 --> 00:17:24.900
These are the new constables from the Chi State Office.

203
00:17:24.900 --> 00:17:28.790
The Lord got hurt badly and Miss Jiang is scared there is a thef.

204
00:17:28.790 --> 00:17:31.830
who will attack our county office. So they're here to protect us.

205
00:17:31.830 --> 00:17:33.960
Sir is in trouble?

206
00:17:33.960 --> 00:17:35.490
He still isn't awake.

207
00:17:35.490 --> 00:17:37.050
I'll go take a look.

208
00:17:42.600 --> 00:17:47.050
Miss Jiang said the Lord needs rest, so he has to rest.

209
00:17:47.050 --> 00:17:50.600
When he is better than she will tell us.

210
00:17:55.800 --> 00:18:00.180
Don't be concerned about things you shouldn't be concerned about. Do the things you have to do.

211
00:18:26.230 --> 00:18:27.840
These

212
00:18:29.020 --> 00:18:31.300
were all found in your room.

213
00:18:31.300 --> 00:18:32.780
What do you mean?

214
00:18:32.780 --> 00:18:34.520
Where did you go yesterday?

215
00:18:34.520 --> 00:18:35.500
You're suspecting me?

216
00:18:35.500 --> 00:18:37.350
Where did you go!

217
00:18:38.810 --> 00:18:40.870
I went to see Zong Yinglin.

218
00:18:41.610 --> 00:18:44.230
He is leaving Tongling.

219
00:18:44.230 --> 00:18:46.070
Nothing more?

220
00:18:47.650 --> 00:18:49.660
Are you sure

221
00:18:49.660 --> 00:18:52.700
it's not to kidnap Qingchen and kill Lord Tang?

222
00:18:52.700 --> 00:18:54.650
Zheng Shaofeng!

223
00:18:56.940 --> 00:19:00.390
He came to see me last night to take me.

224
00:19:00.390 --> 00:19:05.280
He already quit! He didn't do any of these things.

225
00:19:11.110 --> 00:19:13.040
Why are you looking at me like that?

226
00:19:17.310 --> 00:19:22.180
The evidence is conclusive. I have to believe it.

227
00:19:22.920 --> 00:19:27.390
Ruyi, I gave you a chance before.

228
00:19:27.390 --> 00:19:31.830
I waited for you this long, but Tang Tianyuan.

229
00:19:31.830 --> 00:19:34.320
Tang Tianyuan is my brother!

230
00:19:36.850 --> 00:19:41.120
How can you do that to him?

231
00:19:41.120 --> 00:19:45.690
If I said it wasn't me, would you believe me?

232
00:19:47.820 --> 00:19:52.030
