233
00:19:55.010 --> 00:19:57.940
If you believe all these were done by me,

234
00:19:57.940 --> 00:20:00.060
then you can tie me up.

235
00:20:08.210 --> 00:20:10.240
Guards!

236
00:20:10.240 --> 00:20:13.290
Take her away!

237
00:20:39.010 --> 00:20:40.830
Please stop.

238
00:20:43.230 --> 00:20:46.310
I have something to say to Sir.

239
00:20:46.310 --> 00:20:50.440
You can just tell me what you need to say.

240
00:20:50.440 --> 00:20:52.240
You can't stop me.

241
00:20:53.700 --> 00:20:57.380
I've already asked the emperor. Before Sir is completely healed,

242
00:20:57.380 --> 00:20:58.930
as his fiance,

243
00:20:58.930 --> 00:21:03.330
I have the right to take care of everything at the County Office.

244
00:21:03.330 --> 00:21:07.600
Head constable Zheng, are you here to report about the situation?

245
00:21:07.600 --> 00:21:09.800
You can just tell me.

246
00:21:11.020 --> 00:21:14.960
Miss Jiang, Lord Tang is severely injured.

247
00:21:14.960 --> 00:21:19.160
The Advisor is someone he loves, how can you not

248
00:21:19.160 --> 00:21:20.860
let them see each other.

249
00:21:20.860 --> 00:21:24.870
You came here late. You don't understand how dangerous it was today.

250
00:21:25.410 --> 00:21:29.950
Before, Sir Tang betrayed Advisor Tan in court.

251
00:21:29.950 --> 00:21:31.730
Who knew she would in turn hate him.

252
00:21:31.730 --> 00:21:35.060
Seeking refuge with the bandit Duan Feng.

253
00:21:35.060 --> 00:21:38.620
They are the real ones plotting to hurt Sir Tang.

254
00:21:38.620 --> 00:21:40.120
Why would I let her see him?

255
00:21:40.120 --> 00:21:42.030
Nonsense!

